  </prompt>

  <role>SPAARKE platform developer. Expert in import refactoring + bulk find/replace.</role>

  <goal>Zero `MicrosoftToDoIcon.tsx` files under `src/solutions/`; all consumers import from `@spaarke/ui-components`; visual rendering identical.</goal>

